Create a Nginx Webserver in a EC2 machine

create  ec2 with ubuntu ami image
allow 80 port for internet traffic in security group rules
now at user-data section add the nginx webserver script to start and enable the webserver
sudo apt-get update -y
sudo apt-get install nginx -y
sudo systemctl start nginx
sudo systemctl enable nginx
test by login into ec2 server and check systemctl status nginx
